{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-20", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "誠摯邀請", "storyInfo": "阿米婭擊敗了變形者集群這位古老的存在。女妖之主的骨哨響徹在所有王庭，用喪鐘慶祝變形者集群的新生。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在看什麼？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你們的那位魔王，女妖。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你正在面對阿米婭。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我奉勸你仔細考慮自己的行動。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "散去你手中的那些咒術吧。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別緊張，他們已經贏了。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝我們之前的交流吧，變形者，現在我更清楚你有哪些手段了。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那本來就是個被德拉克燒得遍體鱗傷的分身，魔王怎麼會輸。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們確實很高興，在如此之長的歲月之後，我們又見識到了一些新的東西。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種興奮，哪怕只有一絲一毫，我們都已經很久未見了。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自豪吧，女妖，你說服我們了，我們樂於為你們保留這種新的可能，雖然我們依然並不看好這種可能所延伸的方向。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但對於我們而言，最不缺的就是時間與耐心。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在下一個結局，我們還會再相見的。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你接下來會去往哪裡？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們從來不去往何處，我們在所有地方徘徊。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變形者，你之前說，你幾乎窮盡了所有的可能。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你仍有未涉足的領域。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哦？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片大地上所有的事物都在演進，而你向來只是停留在原地，然後模彷出某個演進的結果。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，你從來無法去往任何地方，你已經完成了。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已完成之物當然不可能有寸進。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很有說服力的挑釁，你的建議是什麼？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經猜到了。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報喪女妖，你無愧於你的名號。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新生從滅亡中來。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我們確實從未嘗試過......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離這裡不遠的地方，我們剛剛送別了一位朋友。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說，與其隨波逐流，她寧願放棄生活本身。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們體會到了她的情感，我們看到了她的決然。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她自稱這不過是懦弱的選擇，我們卻感受到了些別的東西。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們之前幾乎無法描述，但我們現在知道了，那亦是某種勇氣。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我們未曾想過的一種勇氣。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，好吧，女妖，我們承認......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們確實開始躍躍欲試起來了。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "搞不好，這是你的無傷大雅的小小陰謀，為自己除去一個敵人的拙劣手段。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們並不在乎。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但也許，這是眾魂借你的口，向我們提出的邀請。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "需要我代勞嗎？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給我們留點體面吧。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你與你背後的喪鐘，該為我們鳴響。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_battlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們很頑強，你們很勇敢，你們可以慶祝一下這場勝利。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這不會是你的真正實力。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line112"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，還不盡興嗎，羅德島的博士？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許只是沒有必要呢？也許我們比你最糟糕的估計......還要瞭解你們呢？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我相信羅德島的安全系統。;......;難道羅德島上也有你的分身？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line119", "option2": "line119", "option3": "line119"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，別那麼緊張，博士。你們那艘船的登船檢查，可沒它看上去的那麼簡單。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，再見吧，各位。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你打算做什麼？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#6$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這副殘破的身軀還能做什麼？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們停在原地......確實已經夠久了。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "37_i12", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "yFrom": 20.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 25.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小小的異族魔王啊，你會前往哪裡？", "name": "變形者集群"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會把這些信任你的人，追隨你的人，保護你的人帶向何方？", "name": "變形者集群"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會像博卓卡斯替說出的那個預言一樣，奴役這片大地上的一切......", "name": "變形者集群"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是向我們證明，只是我們，被歷史束縛得太深？", "name": "變形者集群"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“演進”，這是個狡猾的詞彙，它彷彿預示著必然的進步，當然並非如此。", "name": "變形者集群"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但沒關係，你會找到道路的，我們也一樣。", "name": "變形者集群"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_battlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他消散了......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，變形者不會死去，他的另一個更加完整、更加強大的分身很可能就在附近。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#6$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是他慣用的伎倆，讓獵物放下戒心，再給予致命一擊......", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#6$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_boneflute"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......骨哨聲？這怎麼可能？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#4$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Logos視骨哨為舊王庭可悲的傳統，他從來拒絕像他的那些前任一樣吹響它。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#4$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這確實是喪鐘之主的骨哨。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#10$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#4$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變形者的集群......在死去。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#4$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“挽歌已經響起，骨哨已經哀鳴。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我在此擔當一位薩卡茲的見證者，變形者，他的集群。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“新生自滅亡中來。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_victoria", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_055", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "骨哨聲。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_055", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從這一位女妖之主踐祚王庭，我們已經多久沒有聽過骨哨聲了？", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_062", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_062", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變形者死了。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_055", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擔心，變形者閣下只是迎來了一次小小的挫折，他很快......", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_062", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我的意思是，所有的變形者在同一時刻凋零。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_062", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變形者死去了，最為恒久的王庭就此崩塌。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_062", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哼，真有意思。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_062", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，他自己都沒有想到，會是這個結果。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_062", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我該怎麼形容？一次分裂？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_062", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......還是兩個新生？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g11_wsafehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亙古統一的變形者已經不復存在。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而兩位初生的變形者，出現在了這個世間。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自然界中，黃沙被看做是萬物的盡頭，再堅固的巨石都會在時間的終點化作齏粉。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但說不定，黃沙也同樣擁有重新開始輪迴的可能。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希，你的傷還沒好，小心我向閃靈告狀——", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我已經基本沒事了。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許很快，會有一位老朋友找上我們......不，現在是新朋友了。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一點也不想見到你的任何一位老朋友或者新朋友。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#12$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一個壞消息和一個好消息，你選哪個？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，我真是累昏了頭，怎麼會想起來跟你玩這種蠢遊戲。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#2$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "壞消息是——", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我選好消息。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "壞消息是我們在布倫特伍德沒發現薩卡茲那條補給線的入口到底在哪，根本沒有什麼地下隧道之類的設施，但是又的確有檢修通道......", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，你說......啊？？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，我選好消息。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，呃，我......", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閃靈——", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我偶爾也想聽聽好消息，可露希爾。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好消息是，我們收到博士的聯絡了。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝您的幫助，溫德米爾公爵，我們已經與隊伍重建了聯繫。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們帶出來的這些難民也已經全部登艦，接下來他們會暫時受溫德米爾公爵的庇護。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才要謝謝你們，羅德島。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#8$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們幫助諾伯特區的市民們躲過了一場滅頂之災。雖然不是全部，但是......已經足夠。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#8$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保護國民本應是我們這些肩負公爵之名的人應該幹的事。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#8$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況，你們還救下了我的女兒。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#9$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......她剛剛在房間裡大哭了一場。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#8$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽！我只是......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些日子，我能猜到你們經歷了什麼。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#2$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但也許從那樣的地方走出來，戴菲恩，你才更能瞭解到，掌握權力的人到底應該如何運用自己的力量。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恕我冒昧，公爵閣下，您會如何運用這種力量呢？", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在目睹了蒸汽騎士們的結局後，我不能肯定——", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須得做出決策，孟塔古家的女兒。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以稱呼那為一場陰謀，我不否認，在蒸汽騎士的調令上我也簽了字。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但......決定這個國家的未來，這就是我們的使命。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“使命”。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，“使命”，維娜小姐。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我的稱呼是什麼意思。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和達格達先失陪了，公爵閣下。現在......我更想和我的朋友們待在一起。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請隨意。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#2$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attri