329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩和我說了你們和她的那場交易。雖然中途出了一些波折，但是我姑且肯定那場交易的條件還是達成了。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你不可能真的成為羅德島的支持者。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line334"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我暫時答應你，當做什麼事都沒有發生過。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等到回到我的駐地，我們可以慢慢討論這些。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......卡鐸爾沒有登船，他帶著幾個人離開了。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漢娜呢？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還在房間裡，不願意出來。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再過一會兒，我們去給她送點吃的吧，在諾伯特區，她幾乎沒好好吃過飯。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在燒什麼？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一些草稿罷了。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是以前隨手記下的，為了寫回憶錄積著的靈感。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我忘了把回憶錄本身丟在哪裡了，哈哈。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王，你不需要它，對吧？我們都不需要它了。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......推進之王，你怎麼......你是在哭嗎？", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有，我只是......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大滴的淚水順著推進之王的臉頰滾下，摩根和達格達都愣住了，維娜從不流淚，這是所有人的共識。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在高速戰艦的甲板上，維多利亞的太陽仍在緩緩升起，掃去昨夜的陰霾，烤乾昨夜的濃霧。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這個叫維娜的青年，正背對著太陽，無言地宣洩著自己的情感。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "